Title: 045: Exclusive Interview with the Legendary in Kaggle Competitions Eu Jin Lok
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with Kaggle Grandmaster Eu Jin Lok. You will be able to learn how to forecast year-ahead hospital stays using an ensemble of algorithms, discover feature extraction in a credit scoring model, discuss his great competition experiences, and get ideas on how to be involved in a Kaggle competition.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/45
